{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"act31side_level_act31side_05_beg","storyGroup":"act31side","storySort":10,"storyDependence":"act31side_level_act31side_04_end","storyCanShow":1,"storyCode":"HS-5","storyName":"纺绫罗","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"左乐凭借夕借与的力量将绩困在画卷中，想要迫使这名最大的嫌疑人就范。与此同时，大荒城田地的污染，已经到了难以控制的地步。","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"activities/act31side/level_act31side_05_beg","avgTag":"行动前","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"act31side_05","minState":"PLAYED","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":8,"next":10,"characters":["黍","年迈的女性","疲惫的职农","左乐","绩","天师学徒","禾生"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","id":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":1},{"type":"stopmusic","id":2},{"type":"dialog","id":3},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":4},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e1/Avg_bg_bg_snow_2.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":5},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$distressed_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_distressed_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":6,"musicid":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":7},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":8},{"type":"cameraeffect","effect":"Grayscale","fadetime":"2","keep":"true","initamount":"0","amount":"0.7","block":"true","id":9},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#1$1","duration":"1.5","id":10},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":11},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#2$1","id":12},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"你又要走了。","id":13,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/bc/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1242_1#9$1","id":14},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年迈的女性","text":"这次不劝我了？","id":15,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/af/Avg_avg_npc_1242_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#1$1","id":16},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"你又有哪次听劝了呢。","id":17,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e0/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1242_1#1$1","id":18},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年迈的女性","text":"可没有你唠叨两句，我反而觉得心里空落落的。","id":19,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a5/Avg_avg_npc_1242_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年迈的女性","text":"我还能走得动，胳膊腿都还结实着。春天的风还是这么冷，我也不能躺在椅子上晒太阳。","id":20,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a5/Avg_avg_npc_1242_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#16$1","id":21},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"你该知道，北边有多危险。","id":22,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/cf/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-16$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1242_1#6$1","id":23},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年迈的女性","text":"可是黍......你也知道，我们没有办法......","id":24,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d4/Avg_avg_npc_1242_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年迈的女性","text":"我们花了几十年时间，才开辟出这点土地。可还是远远不够......","id":25,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d4/Avg_avg_npc_1242_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1242_1#1$1","id":26},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年迈的女性","text":"粮食和地总是不够的......再北一点的地方，说不定可以找到特殊的庄稼，可以种在源石污染过的土地上的庄稼。","id":27,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a5/Avg_avg_npc_1242_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年迈的女性","text":"到时候，整片大地都可以当作我们的农田，再也不会有人忍饥挨饿。","id":28,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a5/Avg_avg_npc_1242_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#5$1","id":29},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"那你更应该留下来。","id":30,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5d/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"找不到这种庄稼，我们就慢慢培育。十代，百代，总有一天——","id":31,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5d/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1242_1#3$1","id":32},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年迈的女性","text":"可是，我哪还有那么多时间呢？","id":33,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7c/Avg_avg_npc_1242_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#8$1","id":34},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"......","id":35,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/02/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1242_1#2$1","id":36},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年迈的女性","text":"何况，“种在源石污染土地里的庄稼”“整片大地变成良田”，这样的话，被人听到，只会被当作痴人说梦吧。","id":37,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5e/Avg_avg_npc_1242_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#3$1","id":38},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"......我说不过你。","id":39,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/38/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1242_1#9$1","id":40},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年迈的女性","text":"老人说的话总是更有道理的。","id":41,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/af/Avg_avg_npc_1242_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"text","text":"女性缓缓伸出一只手，手指轻轻地攥着。","id":42},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年迈的女性","text":"黍呀......能不能再请你看看我的手相？看看我这个老婆婆，到底还有没有在晚年实现理想的好运气？","id":43,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/af/Avg_avg_npc_1242_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#1$1","id":44},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"我说过，我不会看的。","id":45,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e0/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1242_1#9$1","id":46},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年迈的女性","text":"......","id":47,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/af/Avg_avg_npc_1242_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"text","text":"女性笑着，伸开手掌，掌心里躺着一朵白色的小花。她将花别在眼前女孩的发髻上。","id":48},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1242_1#9$1","id":49},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年迈的女性","text":"今天我在田里发现了一朵花，应该是今年开的第一朵，我觉得应该是个好兆头。","id":50,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/af/Avg_avg_npc_1242_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年迈的女性","text":"说不定赶在今年收获的时候，我就能回来了。","id":51,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/af/Avg_avg_npc_1242_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年迈的女性","text":"你掐算着日子，炖好排骨汤等着我就好了。","id":52,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/af/Avg_avg_npc_1242_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":53},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":54},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":55},{"type":"sticker","id":56,"text":"黍啊......","x":"500","y":"400","alignment":"center","size":"22","delay":"0.001","width":"700","block":"true","duration":"0.5"},{"type":"sticker","id":57,"duration":"0.5","block":"false"},{"type":"sticker","id":58,"text":"嗯？","x":"0","y":"300","alignment":"center","size":"22","delay":"0.001","width":"700","block":"true","duration":"0.5"},{"type":"sticker","id":59,"duration":"0.5","block":"false"},{"type":"sticker","id":60,"text":"你其实一直都能看到那个未来的，对吧？","x":"500","y":"400","alignment":"center","size":"22","delay":"0.001","width":"700","block":"true","duration":"0.5"},{"type":"sticker","id":61,"duration":"0.5","block":"false"},{"type":"sticker","id":62,"text":"......","x":"0","y":"300","alignment":"center","size":"22","delay":"0.001","width":"700","block":"true","duration":"0.5"},{"type":"sticker","id":63,"duration":"0.5","block":"false"},{"type":"sticker","id":64,"text":"你最后......","x":"0","y":"300","alignment":"center","size":"22","delay":"0.001","width":"700","block":"true","duration":"0.5"},{"type":"sticker","id":65,"duration":"0.5","block":"false"},{"type":"sticker","id":66,"text":"别......别告诉我，我可不想知道自己什么时候会死。","x":"500","y":"400","alignment":"center","size":"22","delay":"0.001","width":"700","block":"true","duration":"0.5"},{"type":"sticker","id":67,"duration":"0.5","block":"false"},{"type":"sticker","id":68,"text":"我只是想问问......","x":"500","y":"400","alignment":"center","size":"22","delay":"0.001","width":"700","block":"true","duration":"0.5"},{"type":"sticker","id":69,"duration":"1","block":"false"},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":70},{"type":"sticker","id":71,"text":"我们那个万顷良田的梦，最后实现了吗？","x":"500","y":"400","alignment":"center","size":"22","delay":"0.001","width":"700","block":"true","duration":"1"},{"type":"sticker","id":72,"duration":"1","block":"false"},{"type":"dialog","id":73},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":74},{"type":"charslot","id":75},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":76},{"type":"cameraeffect","effect":"Grayscale","fadetime":"0","amount":"0","block":"true","id":77},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/52/Avg_bg_47_g1_desertedcityfield_d.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":78},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#4$1","id":79},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":80},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"......","id":81,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/63/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":82},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":83},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":84},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":85},{"type":"dialogue","name":"疲惫的职农","text":"天师......","id":86},{"type":"dialogue","name":"疲惫的职农","text":"黍姑娘？","id":87},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#18$1","id":88},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"欸？","id":89,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/aa/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-18$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":90},{"type":"dialogue","name":"疲惫的职农","text":"黍姑娘，我看您在这里愣了半天了，您肯定也不舍得这片地吧。","id":91},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#2$1","id":92},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"嗯......","id":93,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/bc/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#1$1","id":94},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"山清水秀，粮食可口......我很喜欢这里。","id":95,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e0/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":96},{"type":"dialogue","name":"疲惫的职农","text":"黍天师，您看上去这么年轻，调来大荒城没多久吧。","id":97},{"type":"dialogue","name":"疲惫的职农","text":"我从出生就在这里，现在都六十七了......六十七年，也从来没想过有一天，还得离开这儿。","id":98},{"type":"dialogue","name":"疲惫的职农","text":"听说，从神农她老人家开垦出这片农田，到现在都一千多年了。我们怎么舍得......","id":99},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#1$1","id":100},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"庄稼春种秋收，一年也躲不开风霜雨雪。世事不如意才是常态，我们也只能顺其自然。","id":101,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e0/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"以后搬到移动城市里，大家会有别的活计可做，相信会给大家妥善安排的。","id":102,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e0/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":103},{"type":"dialogue","name":"疲惫的职农","text":"我们就是不明白......本来以为这两年天气差点，所以收成差点，大家加把劲，总能扛过去的。","id":104},{"type":"dialogue","name":"疲惫的职农","text":"可现在告诉我们是这块地出了问题......黍姑娘，你们天师懂的多，你能不能再想想办法，救救这块地？","id":105},{"type":"dialogue","name":"疲惫的职农","text":"您只要告诉我们一个法子，我们也不怕辛苦，哪怕是要把这块地整个翻一遍——","id":106},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#8$1","id":107},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"......","id":108,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/02/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":109},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":110},{"type":"charslot","id":111},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":112},{"type":"dialogue","name":"疲惫的职农","text":"前两天才下过大雨，这土地怎么......","id":113},{"type":"dialog","id":114},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$nervous_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_nervous_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":115,"musicid":1},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_dkmgcvlspd","id":116},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/52/Avg_bg_47_g1_desertedcityfield_d.png","screenadapt":"coverall","fadetime":"4","id":117},{"type":"backgroundtween","xScaleFrom":"1.05","yScaleFrom":"1.05","xScaleTo":"1","yScaleTo":"1","duration":"3.5","block":"false","id":118},{"type":"cameraeffect","effect":"Grayscale","fadetime":"3","keep":"true","initamount":"0","amount":"1","block":"false","id":119},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":120},{"type":"text","text":"田边的职农突然瞪直了眼。","id":121},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_surfacefrozen","id":122},{"type":"text","text":"田间蓄水以肉眼可见的速度消失，仿佛是地底藏着一个无底的深渊，霎时间抽干了田地间所有水分，也抽走了土地的生命力。","id":123},{"type":"text","text":"湿润的水田转瞬间变成了板结的盐碱地，长出了无数深不见底的裂纹。","id":124},{"type":"dialog","id":125},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":126},{"type":"charslot","id":127},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":128},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e2/Avg_bg_47_g4_factory_outside.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":129},{"type":"cameraeffect","effect":"Grayscale","fadetime":"0","amount":"0","block":"true","id":130},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":131},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":132},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":133},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1236_1#1$1","duration":"0.5","id":134},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","posfrom":"-200,0","posto":"0,0","duration":"1.5","id":135},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":136},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1","duration":"0.5","id":137},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":138},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1","focus":"l","id":139},{"type":"dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"站住。","id":140,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/bd/Avg_avg_4121_zuole_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1236_1#9$1","focus":"r","id":141},{"type":"dialogue","name":"绩","text":"左公子。","id":142,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0c/Avg_avg_npc_1236_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1","focus":"l","id":143},{"type":"dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"你准备去哪？","id":144,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/bd/Avg_avg_4121_zuole_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1236_1#9$1","focus":"r","id":145},{"type":"dialogue","name":"绩","text":"送到了该送的东西，见过了想见的人，也该离开了——左公子是来给在下送行？","id":146,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0c/Avg_avg_npc_1236_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1","focus":"l","id":147},{"type":"dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"把所有问题交代清楚前，你还不能走。","id":148,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/bd/Avg_avg_4121_zuole_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1236_1#7$1","focus":"r","id":149},{"type":"dialogue","name":"绩","text":"之前让我离开的是司岁台，现在让我留下的也是司岁台......朝令夕改，在下也很难办啊。","id":150,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a2/Avg_avg_npc_1236_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1","focus":"l","id":151},{"type":"dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"大荒城中出现的邪魔秽物和你有什么关系，你对核心城的装置有什么图谋？","id":152,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/bd/Avg_avg_4121_zuole_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"还有......一百年前，那罪人从京城逃脱，短短数月之后，他的棋子就遍布了炎国各地，你又从中做了什么？！","id":153,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/bd/Avg_avg_4121_zuole_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1236_1#9$1","focus":"r","id":154},{"type":"dialogue","name":"绩","text":"......左公子的这些问题，在下一句都听不明白。","id":155,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0c/Avg_avg_npc_1236_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1","focus":"l","id":156},{"type":"dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"那就押送你去一个能说清楚问题的地方。","id":157,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/bd/Avg_avg_4121_zuole_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1236_1#9$1","focus":"r","id":158},{"type":"dialogue","name":"绩","text":"......","id":159,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0c/Avg_avg_npc_1236_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"绩","text":"左公子孤身前来，的确是勇气可嘉。要不是时间紧张，在下也非常愿意和左公子这样的青年才俊多聊聊。","id":160,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0c/Avg_avg_npc_1236_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1236_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":161},{"type":"dialogue","name":"绩","text":"可是......要是在下不配合呢？","id":162,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d2/Avg_avg_npc_1236_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":163},{"type":"text","text":"男人拿出一只玉梭，除了格外精致些，似乎没有什么异样。","id":164},{"type":"text","text":"左乐看到了上面隐隐绕着的丝线。","id":165},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4121_zuole_1#5$1","id":166},{"type":"dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"休想——！","id":167,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f1/Avg_avg_4121_zuole_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":168},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e2/Avg_bg_47_g4_factory_outside.png","screenadapt":"coverall","xScale":"1.1","yScale":"1.1","fadetime":"1","id":169},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_watersubcreate","volume":"1","id":170},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_xsplashink","volume":"1","delay":"0.2","channel":"s","id":171},{"type":"dialog","id":172},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"1","g":"1","b":"1","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":173},{"type":"charslot","id":174},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1e/Avg_bg_bg_landscape.png","screenadapt":"coverall","xScale":"1.05","yScale":"1.05","id":175},{"type":"delay","time":"0.3","id":176},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1e/Avg_bg_bg_landscape.png","screenadapt":"coverall","fadetime":"2","id":177},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":178},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1236_1#1$1","duration":"0.5","id":179},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":180},{"type":"dialogue","name":"绩","text":"嗯......？","id":181,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d2/Avg_avg_npc_1236_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":182},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","fadeout":"true","xstrength":"25","ystrength":"25","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","block":"false","id":183},{"type":"playsound","key":"$e_skill_skulsrsword","id":184},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.6","r":"1","g":"1","b":"1","fadetime":"0.03","block":"true","id":185},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1","posfrom":"-150,0","posto":"50,0","duration":"0.3","id":186},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","posfrom":"0,0","posto":"50,0","duration":"0.3","id":187},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.6","block":"true","id":188},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":189},{"type":"text","text":"晃神只有一瞬间。","id":190},{"type":"text","text":"男人手中玉梭还未扬起，秉烛人的刀锋已经抵在了他的喉咙上。","id":191},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1","focus":"l","id":192},{"type":"dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"我不过是一个普通人，没有和你们代理人对抗的力量......","id":193,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/bd/Avg_avg_4121_zuole_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"但是在这幅画卷里，我们没有什么区别。","id":194,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/bd/Avg_avg_4121_zuole_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1236_1#6$1","focus":"m","id":195},{"type":"dialogue","name":"绩","text":"这画卷......是我那个妹妹......","id":196,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/80/Avg_avg_npc_1236_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1236_1#4$1","focus":"m","id":197},{"type":"dialogue","name":"绩","text":"你们寻常人类什么时候也敢利用这种力量了？","id":198,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/dd/Avg_avg_npc_1236_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1","focus":"l","id":199},{"type":"dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"你大概是低估了巨兽学士对你们的研究程度......你们每一位的能力，司岁台都了如指掌。","id":200,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/bd/Avg_avg_4121_zuole_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1236_1#3$1","focus":"m","id":201},{"type":"dialogue","name":"绩","text":"没想到夕居然对我意见这么大，宁愿和秉烛人合作也要来找我的麻烦......","id":202,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4a/Avg_avg_npc_1236_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1236_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":203},{"type":"dialogue","name":"绩","text":"不过秉烛人私下接触代理人不该是重罪吗？左公子已经是戴罪之身，还要做这种出格的事，就没有考虑过后果？","id":204,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d2/Avg_avg_npc_1236_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1","focus":"l","id":205},{"type":"dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"能在这里阻止你......将你捉拿归案就够了。","id":206,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/bd/Avg_avg_4121_zuole_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"你将邪魔污染引入大荒城，就是为了毁掉十二楼五城？","id":207,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/bd/Avg_avg_4121_zuole_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"这件事背后，是不是也有那个罪人的谋划？","id":208,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/bd/Avg_avg_4121_zuole_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1236_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":209},{"type":"dialogue","name":"绩","text":"如果我说，正是如此呢？","id":210,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d2/Avg_avg_npc_1236_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4121_zuole_1#5$1","focus":"l","id":211},{"type":"dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"？！","id":212,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f1/Avg_avg_4121_zuole_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1236_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":213},{"type":"dialogue","name":"绩","text":"那左公子想怎么做呢？","id":214,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0c/Avg_avg_npc_1236_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"绩","text":"在这里杀了我，好让京城地底的岁得到的神识再多一份？大炎真的做好开战的准备了？","id":215,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0c/Avg_avg_npc_1236_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1","focus":"l","id":216},{"type":"dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"如果这样才能阻止你，我们会这么做。时至今日，岁兽绝不是你们胡作非为的挡箭牌。","id":217,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/bd/Avg_avg_4121_zuole_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1236_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":218},{"type":"dialogue","name":"绩","text":"可到底是笔需要盘算的买卖。","id":219,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0c/Avg_avg_npc_1236_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":220},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","posfrom":"50,0","posto":"100,0","duration":"0.7","id":221},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":222},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_clothmovement","id":223},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"5","ystrength":"10","vibrato":"5","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":224},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","posfrom":"100,0","posto":"100,-30","duration":"0.7","afrom":"1","ato":"0","id":225},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":226},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":227},{"type":"text","text":"男人微笑着无视抵在喉咙上的长刀，掸了掸衣袍，找了一处石阶坐了下来。","id":228},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1","focus":"l","id":229},{"type":"dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"老实点——","id":230,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/bd/Avg_avg_4121_zuole_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":231},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":232},{"type":"charslot","id":233},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1236_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":234},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":235},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1236_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":236},{"type":"dialogue","name":"绩","text":"何必紧张，既然都已经用这幅画卷困住了我，现在的我不过是个手无缚羽之力的裁缝罢了。左公子难道害怕我飞出去？","id":237,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0c/Avg_avg_npc_1236_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"绩","text":"机会难得，不如来聊一聊吧。","id":238,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0c/Avg_avg_npc_1236_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1","id":239},{"type":"dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"你只该回答我的问题。","id":240,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/bd/Avg_avg_4121_zuole_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1236_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":241},{"type":"dialogue","name":"绩","text":"左公子对藏书阁里那些自己没有权限接触的卷宗，难道就不感到好奇？","id":242,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0c/Avg_avg_npc_1236_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"绩","text":"大好的机会就在眼前，左公子想问的问题应该不止这些吧？","id":243,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0c/Avg_avg_npc_1236_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1","id":244},{"type":"dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"别想耍花样......","id":245,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/bd/Avg_avg_4121_zuole_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1236_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":246},{"type":"dialogue","name":"绩","text":"我们就来算笔账吧。","id":247,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0c/Avg_avg_npc_1236_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":248},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1236_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":249},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":250},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1236_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":251},{"type":"dialogue","name":"绩","text":"算一笔炎国和巨兽的账。","id":252,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d2/Avg_avg_npc_1236_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":253},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":254},{"type":"charslot","id":255},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7a/Avg_bg_47_g8_crestofweir.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":256},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":257},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":258},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":259},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1238_1#2$1","duration":"1.5","id":260},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":261},{"type":"dialogue","name":"天师学徒","text":"......到这里就没有了？","id":262,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/74/Avg_avg_npc_1238_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1238_1#4$1","id":263},{"type":"dialogue","name":"天师学徒","text":"这些被邪魔污染的种子，如果是从那条河上漂过来的，怎么越到城边，污染的痕迹越少......","id":264,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/22/Avg_avg_npc_1238_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"天师学徒","text":"难不成......","id":265,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/22/Avg_avg_npc_1238_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":266},{"type":"text","text":"她掬起一把泥土在手里细细捻着，眉头随即攒成一团。","id":267},{"type":"text","text":"地面隐隐有震动传来，远处新建起的移动地块高低起伏，像是连绵的山脉，又像是荒蛮之物隆起的背脊。","id":268},{"type":"text","text":"钢筋水泥捧起有万年历史的土壤，庞大的造物似是架起了跨越无数岁月的桥。可又有谁知晓这土地万年的痕迹？","id":269},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1238_1#3$1","id":270},{"type":"dialogue","name":"天师学徒","text":"......是你干的吗？","id":271,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/86/Avg_avg_npc_1238_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1238_1#2$1","id":272},{"type":"dialogue","name":"天师学徒","text":"这么多年，都是你不声不响地压制着这一片邪魔......你图什么？","id":273,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/74/Avg_avg_npc_1238_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"天师学徒","text":"哪有你这样的“神仙”......","id":274,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/74/Avg_avg_npc_1238_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":275},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":276},{"type":"charslot","id":277},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1","id":278},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1236_1#9$1","id":279},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1e/Avg_bg_bg_landscape.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":280},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":281},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1236_1#9$1","focus":"r","id":282},{"type":"dialogue","name":"绩","text":"左公子，见过蚕吗？或者至少该听过一个成语，叫“作茧自缚”？","id":283,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0c/Avg_avg_npc_1236_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1","focus":"l","id":284},{"type":"dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"什么意思？","id":285,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/bd/Avg_avg_4121_zuole_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1236_1#9$1","focus":"r","id":286},{"type":"dialogue","name":"绩","text":"我对这些事可是熟得很。","id":287,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0c/Avg_avg_npc_1236_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"绩","text":"那些虫子生长的时候总要渡过一劫，渡得过去的，破茧而出；渡不过去的，生命就在一片昏暗里悄无声息地停止了。","id":288,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0c/Avg_avg_npc_1236_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1","focus":"l","id":289},{"type":"dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"......你在说谁是虫子？","id":290,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/bd/Avg_avg_4121_zuole_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1236_1#9$1","focus":"r","id":291},{"type":"dialogue","name":"绩","text":"如你如我，世间万物。","id":292,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0c/Avg_avg_npc_1236_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1","focus":"l","id":293},{"type":"dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"随你怎么想，但我们可没打算自比虫子。","id":294,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/bd/Avg_avg_4121_zuole_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1236_1#9$1","focus":"r","id":295},{"type":"dialogue","name":"绩","text":"你们以自己创造的文明为荣，可司岁台的资料里，难道没有记述最初的最初，真龙为什么能结束百氏之乱？","id":296,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0c/Avg_avg_npc_1236_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1","focus":"l","id":297},{"type":"dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"我们当然知道，也十分清楚那不过是岁兽出于傲慢的愚弄，绝非恩赐。难道你还想让炎国念你们的好？","id":298,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/bd/Avg_avg_4121_zuole_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"何况时至今日，你们早就不具备那样的力量。","id":299,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/bd/Avg_avg_4121_zuole_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1236_1#9$1","focus":"r","id":300},{"type":"dialogue","name":"绩","text":"毁灭新生，任何生命都逃不过。夏虫不可语冰，我们所见所闻所思所想，其实都被包在一只茧里，总要保持谦逊的。","id":301,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0c/Avg_avg_npc_1236_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1","focus":"l","id":302},{"type":"dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"你想说什么？","id":303,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/bd/Avg_avg_4121_zuole_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1236_1#3$1","focus":"r","id":304},{"type":"dialogue","name":"绩","text":"从那场大战结束，我们这些人出现，司岁台至今也有千年的历史了。","id":305,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4a/Avg_avg_npc_1236_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1236_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":306},{"type":"dialogue","name":"绩","text":"左公子难道就没有考虑过，为什么直到现在炎国才决定除岁？","id":307,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d2/Avg_avg_npc_1236_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1","focus":"l","id":308},{"type":"dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"百年前，那罪人作乱，导致一名代理人身死。如今岁兽苏醒已是不可避免，除岁当然势在必行。","id":309,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/bd/Avg_avg_4121_zuole_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1236_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":310},{"type":"dialogue","name":"绩","text":"岁兽将醒，是哪位巨兽学士得出的结论？","id":311,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d2/Avg_avg_npc_1236_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1","focus":"l","id":312},{"type":"dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"......","id":313,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/bd/Avg_avg_4121_zuole_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1236_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":314},{"type":"dialogue","name":"绩","text":"待到炎国不得不大动干戈时，到底对谁有利好，“除岁”这件事，有没有某些人自己的算盘？","id":315,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d2/Avg_avg_npc_1236_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"绩","text":"这些问题，左公子到底是没想过，还是假装它们不存在？","id":316,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d2/Avg_avg_npc_1236_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1","focus":"l","id":317},{"type":"dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"我凭什么要听信你的一面之词......","id":318,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/bd/Avg_avg_4121_zuole_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1236_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":319},{"type":"dialogue","name":"绩","text":"当然不必信我，我们来算另一笔账吧。","id":320,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d2/Avg_avg_npc_1236_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"绩","text":"且不论我只是一介商贩走卒，我那些年长的哥哥姐姐数百年来把多少危险挡在大炎国门之外。","id":321,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d2/Avg_avg_npc_1236_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"绩","text":"就连我那个“游手好闲”的妹妹，要是没有她，炎国不知道要花多少倍的力气才能造出如今这些移动城市。","id":322,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d2/Avg_avg_npc_1236_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1236_1#3$1","focus":"r","id":323},{"type":"dialogue","name":"绩","text":"还有，一直守在这里的那位姐姐......","id":324,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4a/Avg_avg_npc_1236_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"绩","text":"巨兽与炎国的历史共生，自始至终，我的那些兄弟姐妹不曾做过危害炎国的事，他们所求，不过只是像人一样普通地活着罢了。","id":325,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4a/Avg_avg_npc_1236_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1236_1#4$1","focus":"r","id":326},{"type":"dialogue","name":"绩","text":"而如今，他们却要因为一些无妄之灾丢了性命......左公子倒是告诉我，这笔账又该怎么算？","id":327,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/dd/Avg_avg_npc_1236_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4121_zuole_1#6$1","focus":"l","id":328},{"type":"dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"......","id":329,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f5/Avg_avg_4121_zuole_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4121_zuole_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":330},{"type":"dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"你们当中有些人，的确对炎国功不可没，炎国也从来不曾忘记。","id":331,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f0/Avg_avg_4121_zuole_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1","focus":"l","id":332},{"type":"dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"现在，是你们中有人选择站在了与大炎敌对的一面，是你们在威胁大炎亿兆百姓的安全。","id":333,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/bd/Avg_avg_4121_zuole_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1236_1#9$1","focus":"r","id":334},{"type":"dialogue","name":"绩","text":"哎，左公子方才还说，所谓“神”对炎国的照顾不过尔尔，怎么遇到一些难题，便又怪起“神”了？","id":335,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0c/Avg_avg_npc_1236_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"绩","text":"哪里有“神”呢，自始至终，都只有人。","id":336,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0c/Avg_avg_npc_1236_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"绩","text":"为什么不看看你们自己脚下呢。","id":337,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0c/Avg_avg_npc_1236_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"3","id":338},{"type":"dialog","id":339},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":340},{"type":"charslot","id":341},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":342},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/8a/Avg_bg_bg_black.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":343},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_gatecloz","id":344},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":345},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":346},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":347},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4119_wanqin_1#2$1","duration":"1.5","id":348},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":349},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4119_wanqin_1#7$1","id":350},{"type":"dialogue","name":"禾生","text":"这些受污染的庄稼，不是已经处理掉了......","id":351,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a7/Avg_avg_4119_wanqin_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4119_wanqin_1#8$1","id":352},{"type":"dialogue","name":"禾生","text":"不，不对......这些明明是之前正常收下来的粮食，为什么会变成这样......","id":353,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/29/Avg_avg_4119_wanqin_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$plot_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_plot_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":354,"musicid":2},{"type":"charslot","duration":"1","id":355},{"type":"text","text":"几日前收割下来的稻谷堆满了粮仓。","id":356},{"type":"text","text":"本应是金黄色的谷堆，现在却变成了赤黑色的小山。","id":357},{"type":"dialog","id":358},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":359},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":360},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":361},{"type":"image","id":362},{"type":"charslot","id":363}],"characters":["黍","年迈的女性","疲惫的职农","左乐","绩","天师学徒","禾生"]}